ng evidence of a conventional mechanism. However, the unusually\nstrong optical phonon suggests a contribution of electronic degrees of freedom.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 20 Dec 2016 16:18:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 30 Dec 2016 00:02:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-10-11"}
