rocesses, the radiation and winds from massive stars and accreting\nblack holes, an accurate treatment of supernova explosions as well as the\nnon-thermal components of the interstellar medium like magnetic fields and\ncosmic rays.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 20 Dec 2016 21:45:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-08-30"}
