 by Dopico, Lawrence, P\\'erez and Van Dooren, and share with it\nits key features, namely, it is a rigorous analysis valid for finite\nperturbations, i.e., it is not a first order analysis, it provides precise\nbounds, and it is valid simultaneously for a large class of\nstructure-preserving strong linearizations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 21 Dec 2016 08:33:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-12-22"}
