ason we provide fits of\nour calculated rate constants that allow the inclusion of these reactions in\nmodels in a straightforward fashion.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 21 Dec 2016 09:32:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-03-15"}
